name: China_insta_girl
description:
This LoRA is based on a model created by Stable Diffusion, not a real person.

Trigger word is 1girl. so if you want multiple girls, recommend use controlnet.

My example images used ChilloutMix.(Base model too.)

Example images contains EXIF.

Hope you enjoy, and feedback is always welcome.

If this LoRa has any problems, i will erase this LoRA and no more updates.

If you have any questions or requests, please contact my Twitter account.
